        ],
        "derivation": "x(x+1) + 8 = (x+2)(x-2) \\implies x^2 + x + 8 = x^2 - 4 \\implies x + 12 = 0 \\text{ (Linear). } (x+2)^2 = 2(x+3) \\implies x^2 + 4x + 4 = 2x + 6 \\implies x^2 + 2x - 2 = 0"
      },
